<title>USA: Seagram unit names Preston VP of finance.</title>
<headline>Seagram unit names Preston VP of finance.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1996-11-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Seagram Co Ltd said on Friday that John Preston was named vice president of finance of Joseph E. Seagram &amp; Sons Inc, Seagram Co's U.S. beverage subsidiary, effective February 1, 1997.</p>
<p>Preston, whose position is newly created, will also assume temporary responsibilities of treasurer Jeananne Hauswald, who will be leaving the company on June 30, 1997, Seagram said.</p>
<p>In the last two years, Preston has helped integrate Seagram with its 80 percent acquisition of MCA Inc, an entertainment company, Seagram said.</p>
